This directory contains Platform Support Packages for various platforms

For any platform, there is a common part, and there can be platform
specific parts. The common part need to be always "applied". The
platform specific part needs to be applied when it is provided.

What "applied" means is described in the common/README file.

The Makefile in this directory is assisting the creation of the
package for release, and is typically invoked as

    make pkg


